.DT
shout
Discworld player help
shout

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
shout - Shout a message to all the players.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
shout
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Shout is a way of giving a message to all players in your vicinity on
the mud.  When you shout a message, all players in your vicinity are
given the message in the following format.  If your name is Lynscar and
you type 'shout How do I use pf's soul?', all players near you would receive
the message.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> shout How do I use pf's soul?
You shout asking: How do I use pf's soul?

Everyone near you sees
Lynscar shouts asking: How do I use pf's soul?

Pinkfish shouts: what is your problem?  It is easy to use!

Furball shouts: Give up now.  Pinkfish is the only one who knows how!

Ember shouts: I agree with furball (for once ;)
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
frimble, lsay, say, sayto, soul, tell, whisper.
.EP
